OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1779995467
OL,3,CUnauthorised airport car parks make
OL,4,Cvillages 'unliveable', say residents
OL,6,FResidents living near Bristol Airport
OL,7,Fsay they are "suffering immeasurably"
OL,8,Fbecause of the rising problem of
OL,9,Funauthorised car parks, problematic
OL,10,Fstreet parking and anti-social
OL,11,Fbehaviour.
OL,13,FThey say the surrounding villages and
OL,14,Fhamlets have become, at times,
OL,15,F"unliveable" as people seek to avoid
OL,16,Fpaying high drop off parking fees at
OL,17,Fthe airport.
OL,26,@oD@eO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
