PN,43102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1779995467
OL,3,CUnauthorised airport car parks make
OL,4,Cvillages 'unliveable', say residents
OL,6,FBristol Airport wants to increase its
OL,7,Fannual passenger capacity to 15
OL,8,Fmillion and expand its on-site parking
OL,9,Fby another 2000 spaces.
OL,11,FBut residents say this will force even
OL,12,Fmore traffic into their communities.
OL,14,FSimon Martin, who has lived in Winford
OL,15,Ffor more than 30 years, said: "We've
OL,16,Fhad five or six car parks springing up
OL,17,Faround recently. They cause a great
OL,18,Fissue because people are coming and
OL,19,Fgoing 24 hours a day."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1779995467
OL,3,CUnauthorised airport car parks make
OL,4,Cvillages 'unliveable', say residents
OL,6,FHe added: "People also dump their cars
OL,7,Fin the middle of the high street. All
OL,8,Fthe local people are suffering
OL,9,Fimmeasurably. It's becoming
OL,10,Funliveable."
OL,12,FAnother resident living near an
OL,13,Funauthorised car park in Barrow Gurney
OL,14,Fsaid: "It is disheartening to see
OL,15,Fhundreds of cars move from field to
OL,16,Ffield for five to six months of the
OL,17,Fyear.
OL,26,@vD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1779995467
OL,3,CUnauthorised airport car parks make
OL,4,Cvillages 'unliveable', say residents
OL,6,F"Our little lane gets used as an exit
OL,7,Ffor vehicles; their alarms go off, and
OL,8,Fwe hear swearing and shouting from
OL,9,Ftheir delivery collection people and
OL,10,Fthe loud music from their cars. People
OL,11,Fshow no consideration to those who
OL,12,Flive here."
OL,14,FNorth Somerset Council says it is
OL,15,Fclamping down on unauthorised car
OL,16,Fparks with "record levels" of
OL,17,Fenforcement action.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1779995467
OL,3,CUnauthorised airport car parks make
OL,4,Cvillages 'unliveable', say residents
OL,6,FThey have issued 35 enforcement
OL,7,Fnotices since 2024. But they say this
OL,8,Fis an issue which has doubled in the
OL,9,Flast decade.
OL,11,FCllr Annemieke Waite, Cabinet Member
OL,12,Ffor Planning and Environment, said:
OL,13,F"It has been getting worse - the
OL,14,Fnumber of flights are increasing and
OL,15,Fpeople still prefer to drive to the
OL,16,Fairport than take sustainable
OL,17,Ftransport. There is huge pressure on
OL,18,Fthe area when it comes to where people
OL,19,Fpark their cars."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1779995467
OL,3,CUnauthorised airport car parks make
OL,4,Cvillages 'unliveable', say residents
OL,6,FWe joined Cllr Waite on an inspection
OL,7,Fof a car park that has popped up near
OL,8,FFelton.
OL,10,FShe explains how rogue operators are
OL,11,Fusing permitted development rights,
OL,12,Fwhich means they can legally operate a
OL,13,Fcar park for 28 days before moving to
OL,14,Fuse another field and evading
OL,15,Fenforcement action.
OL,17,FShe is calling on the government to
OL,18,F"step up" and introduce new
OL,19,Flegislation.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1779995467
OL,3,CUnauthorised airport car parks make
OL,4,Cvillages 'unliveable', say residents
OL,6,FCllr Waite said: "Currently we have an
OL,7,Fissue that most sites can operate on a
OL,8,F28 day ruling that means they can use
OL,9,Fa field for 28 days under permitted
OL,10,Fdevelopment rights. At the end of that
OL,11,Fthey have to move the cars. Then they
OL,12,Fjust move to another field so the
OL,13,Foperators are very clever and they
OL,14,Fmove from here to somewhere else to
OL,15,Fsomewhere else. For us that's why we
OL,16,Fneed some extra powers that we
OL,17,Fcurrently don't have."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1779995467
OL,3,CUnauthorised airport car parks make
OL,4,Cvillages 'unliveable', say residents
OL,6,FThe government says it is keeping
OL,7,Fpermitted development rights under
OL,8,Freview but insists, "councils have
OL,9,Fpowers to protect their local area by
OL,10,Fensuring that a planning application
OL,11,Fwill always be required for a
OL,12,Ftemporary car park."
OL,14,FDave Lees, Chief Executive, Bristol
OL,15,FAirport, added: "In 2024 we committed
OL,16,Fto fully funding an extra parking
OL,17,Fplanning enforcement officer at North
OL,18,FSomerset Council for two years and
OL,19,Fit's encouraging to see the results
OL,20,Fand positive impact this is having for
OL,21,Flocal communities.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1779995467
OL,3,CUnauthorised airport car parks make
OL,4,Cvillages 'unliveable', say residents
OL,6,F"We've heard firsthand from some of
OL,7,Four neighbours that this is helping
OL,8,Fand stopping some of the rogue
OL,9,Foperators in their tracks.
OL,11,F"We are continuing to work closely
OL,12,Fwith North Somerset Council and intend
OL,13,Fto continue supporting their work, to
OL,14,Fprevent further operators from popping
OL,15,Fup, while deterring existing
OL,16,Funauthorised activity.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,432,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F431A1779995467
OL,3,CUnauthorised airport car parks make
OL,4,Cvillages 'unliveable', say residents
OL,6,F"We also welcome more joint days of
OL,7,Faction with Avon and Somerset police.
OL,8,FThe Airport will continue to work
OL,9,Fclosely with the local communities and
OL,10,Fparish councils most affected."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
